The Virgin experience days Gift Card is the perfect way to treat someone without having to choose a specific experience. Whether they are an adrenalin junkie or aspiring to be the next master chef or maybe they have always

wanted to try something different like Aqua Sphering but never actually got around to doing it, well there is now no excuse. The recipient will also have the choice of choosing more than one experience, so they have the option if they

would like to share their memorable day with a friend or a loved one.


In essence the Gift Card product offers:

• Any value loading of between £10-£500

• Funky gift card packaging

• Access to 1000+ experiences

• Online & telephone redemption

• Unlimited access to 2 for 1’s & other special offers

• 12 months expiry